properties.name: NPPL 2008 Super 7 World Series of Paintball in Huntington Beach
properties.description: Posted by Admacisaac  The National Professional Paintball League (NPPL) is kicking off the first event of the 2008 Super 7 World Series of Paintball in Huntington Beach, California. The 220 top paintball teams from around the world will be competing March 28th - 30th on six fields set up on the beach just south of the famous Pier Plaza and over 50,000 spectators are expected to attend.

properties.name: NPPL 2008 Super 7 World Series of Paintball in Jacksonville, Florida
properties.description: Posted by Admacisaac ALLTEL Stadium Jacksonville FloridaNPPL 2008 Second event happening May 16 - 18, 2008. The ALLTEL Stadium, located in downtown Jacksonville, is home to the Jacksonville Jaguars and is one of the largest stadiums in the NFL. With plenty of sunshine and the backdrop of the Jacksonville skyline as it meets the water, this stadium will be the perfect event to film season 2 of "Xtreme Paintball" on Fox Sports Net.

properties.name: PSP 2008 Chicago Open
properties.description: Posted by Admacisaac Paintball Sports Promotions is excited to announce that the 2008 Chicago Open will be returning to the Bolingbrook Recreation and Aquatic Center June 25th-29th. After three hugely successful events held at BRAC, we’re looking forward to returning for a fourth year.

properties.name: PSP 2008 Phoenix Open
properties.description: Posted by Admacisaac University of Phoenix GlendalePaintball Sports Promotions is excited to announce our first event of the season, the 2008 Phoenix Open. The event will be held March 13th-16th at the Glendale Youth Soccer Complex at the University of Phoenix Stadium in Glendale, AZ.
